{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658740/extras/Your_Island.png?t=1698323321\" /><br><br>Embark on an epic adventure in 'Island of Mine', a magical realm filled with mysteries, treasures, and dangers. Your quest is to restore the island's original form using enchanted crystals while crafting, building villages, and conquering treacherous dungeons. Guided by Eldwood the Wise, acquire sacred artifacts hidden in perilous temples to avert impending darkness. Prepare your skills and equipment for the challenges ahead. Unveil secrets, revive magic, and shape the island's destiny. Are you the chosen one? Experience the allure of 'Island of Mine' today!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658740/extras/Unlock.png?t=1698323321\" /><br><br>Acquire new islands and step into the unknown! Who knows what awaits you on the next island? Perhaps a valuable resource like ore, trees, or a friendly farm animal?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658740/extras/Example.png?t=1698323321\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658740/extras/Diverse_Landscapes.png?t=1698323321\" /><br><br>Discover diverse landscapes in Island of Mine \u2013 from lush Grasslands to serene Forests, sun-kissed Beaches, and magical Winters.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658740/extras/Landscapes.png?t=1698323321\" /><br><br>Each biome holds unique treasures and surprises, inviting you to embark on a delightful adventure!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1698323321","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658740/page.bg.jpg?t=16983233